{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_ling_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_ling_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"醒时梦长","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"初到尚蜀，为了寻一处僻静地小睡，半醉的令来到这山巅古亭。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_ling_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["酒馆伙计","石匠","令","墨魉","器伥","器伥&墨魉","？？？","“岁相”"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"《醒时梦长》","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g09_teahouse","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","volume":"0.8","loop":"true","channel":"bse","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"老哥，你的烂肉面，趁热！","id":12},{"type":"SoundVolume","channel":"bse","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"烫烫烫！","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"这位客官，您要的归行老酒只剩了半坛，再说这酒烈了些，这是小店新到的湖松酒，前晌刚启窖，您看......","id":17},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"character","id":19},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#7$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":21},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"......嗯。","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"向来是客挑酒，几时有酒挑客？这尚蜀的规矩，未免与别处不同。","id":24},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"这......","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"这新酒可能解渴？","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"能。湖松酒清甜滑喉，入口绵长——","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"可能醉人？","id":32},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"这就要看您喝多少了，是酒都能醉人。","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我也不知，你见我醉了，不再上就是。","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"（欸，不像本地人啊。）","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"（看她的打扮和气度，想必是哪个富贵人家游山玩水，来尚蜀寻消遣吧。）","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"（话说，我这几天连着做同一个梦......）","id":42},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"（那我昨天还梦见和小慧成亲了呢！）","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"（赶紧吃你的烂肉面，别耽误上工。）","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"说来听听。","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"啊？","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"梦。","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"呀，客官，我们瞎嘀咕，打扰您喝酒了。","id":53},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"独饮无聊，我请你喝酒，你把梦说与我听。","id":55,"figure":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"您是......解梦师吗？我听说大炎别的地方有专门帮人解梦的行当。","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"......","id":59,"figure":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"那我权当给您解个闷吧。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"我这几天，好几次梦到附近天灾频发，人心惶惶，天师府连降多道令牌，任命我为总督造，负责尚蜀移动城市的改建。","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"信使找到我的时候，我正在雕石头——","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"改建移动城市？","id":65,"figure":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"是的。您一路来应该已经发现了，尚蜀的移动城市是与别处不同的。","id":67,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"将群山挪移至移动平台，这在其他地方无法想象，尚蜀的移动城市可谓巧夺天工。","id":69,"figure":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"正因为这样，我们的承重也超出了常规移动平台的好几倍，机动性大打折扣。","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"要不是老天护佑，尚蜀人杰地灵，极少有天灾，移动城市自建成起并未真的移动过，它还真不一定经得起检验。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"有几分道理。","id":74,"figure":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"但那个梦！我在那个梦里找到了解决的办法！","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"我当上总督造后，这个着急啊......突然在泡茶时得到了启发。","id":77,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"大炎江河连川，百川又归海，这四通八达的水路本身便是移动城市天然的运行轨道。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"况且，常言道“水可载舟”，水流还能与移动城市的动力系统结合，解决承重过大而机动性不足的问题。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":80},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"character","id":82},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"试想，若天灾突降，百年山城却轻如羽毛，快如长箭，顺江而迁。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":84},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"百姓安坐在家中煮茶，只是偶尔风起浪卷，打湿了三山十八峰，晴空大雨，才恍然发现不知不觉间已去千里。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":85},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"到那时，尚蜀将真正不畏天灾，民生安泰。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":86},{"type":"subtitle","id":87},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"倒真是个壮观的梦！我那个妹妹要是在，想必又能得一幅新画。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":92},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"哈哈哈你这个梦唯一真实的地方就只有雕石头！","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"别的怎么就不真了？","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"改建移动城市......你这是把自己当土木天师了啊。","id":98,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"......","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"倒也无妨。","id":102,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"土木天师，想来最开始，也是要从这样的梦做起的。","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"谁又想雕一辈子石头呢......难道你想当一辈子伙计？","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"（嘘！当心点，别让我们掌柜的听到。）","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"我觉得挺好的嘞，客人们来来去去，五湖四海的，有趣得很。虽然起早贪黑，苦是苦了点，但逢年过节，掌柜的也不曾亏待了我们。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"攒一攒，等过个一年半载，我说不定就能把小慧娶回家了。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"那你可得抓点紧。小慧虽然家境一般，但长得好看，我可听说已经有人向她提了亲......","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"锤子——哪个不开眼的。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"哈哈哈哈！","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"不过保不齐你真的能当上土木天师呢......","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"你这梦要成了真，那就不是蜀道难，而是蜀道通了。到时咱们山城的石雕和茶叶能卖到大炎的任何地方。不，不光是大炎。","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"说了半天，忘了问解梦师我这个梦到底怎么回事了。连着做，总觉得不太寻常......","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我并未说自己会解梦。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我也只是常做梦而已。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你要想听，我也可以......","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"那还是——","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_303_1#1$1","id":128},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"酒馆伙计","text":"哎呀，已经过了你平时上工的时辰了，赶紧把账结了回去。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"呀！","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"呀！今天来得急，身上没带......","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"一并算在我的酒资里，也不能白听你一个梦。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"这怎么好意思......","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"多打听一个事，这尚蜀三山十八峰，哪一处最幽僻，最称得上“蜀道难”的说法？","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"石匠","text":"您是要？","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"酒喝够了，想寻个安静地儿睡上一觉，兴许也能做个如你这般有趣的梦。","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":144},{"type":"Dialog","id":145},{"type":"Character","id":146},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":147},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g06_mountainroad_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":148},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"$warm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":149,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":150},{"type":"Text","text":"书生梦马簪金花，女娥梦桥生红药，世人所谓“梦”者，发乎事，起乎情。那个石匠的梦，也是此理。","id":151},{"type":"Text","text":"梦是好梦，但以为它关乎吉凶，随随便便做了，却不敢随随便便解。","id":152},{"type":"Text","text":"梦终究只是梦，过往将来，终是由己。","id":153},{"type":"dialog","id":154},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","id":155},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们怎么在此？","id":158},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"character","id":160},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spiritwhoosh","id":161},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_143#2","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","fadetime":"1.5","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"嘎......","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"是夕让你们这些小家伙来迎我，还是我已然入了她的画中......","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_143#2","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"嘎嘎......","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"抑或......我只是有了醉意？","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"刚刚说到哪儿了？","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"你说你羡慕我。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们这些小家伙居然会说话......","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"好吧，湖松酒都有这般后劲，下次该试试归行老酒。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"墨兄，想来这天地间，和我殊途同归的，也就只有你了。但你终归要比我自在得多哟。","id":179,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"这是哪儿的话？","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"器皿本是死物，无心无念，只不过意外受到令的点染，化成了伥。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"缺柄少盖的茶壶，生出来的伥同样缺胳膊断腿。薄薄青瓷的伥，同样耐不住几下摔打......","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"伥的形与意，都局限在器皿本身了。本体怎样，我们便只能怎样。","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"我们也同样只存在于夕的画卷之中，未必就算得上“活物”。","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"夕的画卷，已然是另一方天地了......你们虽然是随笔涂鸦而成，但和那画中的无限风光一样，都是夕的“念想”啊。","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"“念想”是最无拘束的。有形的时候，一叶扁舟，千江叠浪，枯树生花，华发再青，天地颠倒，万象迷离。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你从哪儿知道的这些词......","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"无形的时候，滴墨不染，搁笔留白，都自有意义。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"夕的念想不停，画卷不收，你们便永远自由自在。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"......","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"听得出来你着实羡慕得紧啊。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"嘎嘎，器兄，我反倒觉得你才值得羡慕。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"哦？","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"自由自在，未见得就是好啊。","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"我问你，这里好几只墨魉，你能分得清哪只是夕喜悦时所涂，哪只是夕伤怀时所涂吗？","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"......你们都长得差不多。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"对啊，我们甚至不知道，夕在涂抹我们时，是何种心情，或者她就是......无情无感。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"可拿你来说吧，你通体古褐色，但肚腹黢黑，那是冲茶煮茶十多年留下的茶渍。你还没靠近，我就仿佛闻到了茶香。","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"诗画之伥附庸风雅，兵戈之伥嗜好杀伐，水火不侵的伥，我们便知它的本体必然经受过长久的火炼窑烧。","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"你们生来便有根可循，是限制，可未尝不是归宿，这正是你们的意义啊。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"见器伥便能见器物本身，更能见使器物的人。甚至器伥虽死，器物本身却还在。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"而墨魉呢，只是无根的风，吹过来晃过去。夕不喜不安时，便能把画都撕了，更何况那画上的几抹涂鸦。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"器兄，这样无根的自由，你还羡慕吗？","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"我依然觉得......","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","focus":"2","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"这样吧，咱俩谁也辩不过谁，正好令在这，请她做个评断吧。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"令不要偏袒就是了。","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们总算想起我了......争得口渴了吧？我这边还剩几坛子湖松酒，正好解渴。","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_143#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_143#2","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"（咕咚咕咚）","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"（咕咚咕咚）","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":228},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":229},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":230},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"欸你别吐啊！","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"咽不下去咽不下去，喉咙烧得慌，我滴个天爷。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"夕是不饮酒的，她怕睡着了做梦......那小墨魉你也应该喝不了吧？","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_143#2","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"（咕咚咕咚）","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"没有呀，我觉得挺好喝的，清甜滑喉，入口绵长。","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"晕乎乎的，像是夕翻转了画......难怪都说炎国人喜欢这玩意儿。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"哈哈哈，确实是个好东西。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我甚爱酒，南方的桃梅晚酿喝过，北方的烈刀子也喝过，可受我点染的器伥，却连一口酒都咽不下去。","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"滴酒不沾的夕，她所画的墨魉偏偏觉得此味甚妙。","id":244,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们可有所思？","id":245,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥&墨魉","text":"......","id":247,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们确实是我和夕的造物，得了几分形意。但几分的我，便已然不是我了，二者终究是有区别的。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"器伥非器，墨魉非墨。你们，难道不都是自己吗？","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥&墨魉","text":"......","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"再者，到底何谓“自由”？","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们觉得我和夕是否自由？","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_143#2","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"墨魉","text":"令自然是自由的——","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"是吗......","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥","text":"难道不是？","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我也不知。","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"真自在者，不知何为自在。","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你们越是苦苦纠结，越是不得其解。本就是自在之物，又何苦自寻烦恼？","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_143#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"器伥&墨魉","text":"......","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"还是不解？","id":269,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"呀，既然不解，索性都散了吧，别挡了路。","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":271},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_306_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_143#1","id":272},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":273},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spiritwhoosh","id":274},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1.5","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":276},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#7$1","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"浪费了我几口酒......","id":278},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"常言道“蜀道难”，果然不虚。盘旋回折，耸峭入云，山路转弯，竟又是一段山路。","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"也罢，想来到山巅时，正好一场好眠。","id":281},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":282},{"type":"Dialog","id":283},{"type":"playSound","key":"$tactfulboost","volume":"0.7","id":284},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_landscape","screenadapt":"coverall","id":286},{"type":"Character","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"Text","text":"看来又是一场诗会。","id":289},{"type":"Text","text":"白瓷的杯子顺水而下，杯中酒与泉流浑然一色。酒杯停在谁处，即须成诗三句。笔力不逮者，衔杯作揖，是谓“流觞”。","id":290},{"type":"Text","text":"酒是桃梅晚酿，采早开的桃蕊，与存好的晚梅一并捣碎入酒，清冽甘甜，入口生津。","id":291},{"type":"Text","text":"那酒的滋味，妙绝。","id":292},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$newhope02_intro","key":"$newhope02_loop","volume":"0.4","id":293,"musicid":2},{"type":"Text","text":"采菱的少女把满满一兜菱角倒进船舱，却不留神将船桨踢飞了出去，脆生生的呼叫声传出去数里远。","id":294},{"type":"Text","text":"春夏之交的雨下了半月还未停，在石板路上砸起的雾气渺若轻烟，相邻的人家隔着雨幕抱怨说厅堂几时能干燥些。","id":295},{"type":"Text","text":"好茶者斗茶，好酒者斗酒，好钓者斗钓，富者斗金玉，贫者斗鸣虫......","id":296},{"type":"Text","text":"哦对了，还有灯会，那可比流觞热闹得多了，造型各异的花灯从街的这头燃到那头，逢着佳节更是彻夜不灭。","id":297},{"type":"Text","text":"移一步可得一句，看一景可得一诗，所以那些年的诗会，我从未输过。","id":298},{"type":"Text","text":"一江烟水一芰荷，酒招深处浣清波。","id":299},{"type":"Text","text":"倒卧西山翠，千年醒回舟。","id":300},{"type":"Text","text":"世情旖旎，酣醉酩酊，何妨衰病减心情。","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"尽兴吗？","id":302},{"type":"dialog","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":304},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"尽兴。","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"......","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"尽兴是尽兴，可就是太容易尽兴了。","id":308},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","focus":"-1","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"厌倦一样事，便对百样事都觉得新鲜。只是这新鲜到头，终究还是厌倦。","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"令，这里不是你的归宿。","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"何不听我的，走得远些去看看。","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你所谓“春风不至”的地方？","id":314},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","focus":"-1","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"是了。","id":316},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"又有什么不同？","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","focus":"-1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"去了便知。","id":320},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#9$1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"那里便是我的归宿了？","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#9$1","focus":"-1","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我也不知。","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"流觞诗会少一个令不少，多一个令不多。可我让你去的地方，需要你。","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"或许你在那里，才能写出，新的诗来。","id":326},{"type":"Dialog","id":327},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"coverall","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":330},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":332},{"type":"Text","text":"那座移动城市。","id":333},{"type":"Text","text":"那座横在大漠前的移动城市。","id":334},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","id":335},{"type":"Text","text":"即使数百年过去，我依然记得初见它时的震撼。此刻，我竟然又站在了它的城楼上。","id":336},{"type":"Text","text":"大漠绵延千里，风沙蒸腾起热浪，云烟浩渺，我能感受到皮肤在急速失去水分。","id":337},{"type":"Text","text":"为了控制水源，它在建造时并未考虑占据险要地势，依山脉以为屏障，而是临近草甸和湖泊。","id":338},{"type":"Text","text":"如此一来，干燥的风扫过无遮无挡的大漠，直扑在城墙上。它像个孤独的巨人，巍巍然矗立在天地间，身无可依。","id":339},{"type":"Text","text":"旌旗漫卷，长河落日。","id":340},{"type":"Text","text":"城关外，战士们正将昨日死难兄弟的尸体搬运出来，一排排码放好，我挨个走过，将他们的眼睛合上。","id":341},{"type":"Text","text":"昨日的连场血战犹在耳畔。遮天蔽日的箭，晴空似夜，杀声如裂帛，经久不绝。","id":342},{"type":"Text","text":"火炬在他们身下点燃，无人哀哭，因为新的战斗将近。烟尘滚滚，但迅速被风吹进茫茫大漠。","id":343},{"type":"Text","text":"......","id":344},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","id":345},{"type":"Text","text":"诗酒已然帮我忘却了许多我曾厌倦的东西，可在此般景象面前，我反应过来时，却已重新握紧了武器。","id":346},{"type":"Text","text":"因为身边的每一个将士，都握紧了武器。","id":347},{"type":"Text","text":"不能让那些家伙，靠近身后的大炎。那是他们的家乡，那里有他们的亲人。","id":348},{"type":"Text","text":"横在这茫茫大漠前的，不是这座巨人般的移动城市，而是这城里的将士。","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","id":350},{"type":"Text","text":"孤城听征鼓，年岁莫问，但凭豪气多。","id":351},{"type":"Text","text":"谁言将军有死志，故垒新柳年年生。","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"他说的没错......我是应该来此的。","id":353},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":354},{"type":"Dialog","id":355},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":356},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g07_fairyland_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":357},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":358},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"$newhope01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":359,"musicid":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你竟然也来了，看来真是梦了。","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":362},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":364},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"别吼了，我方才喝了几坛子湖松酒，头晕着哩。","id":366},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#6$1","focus":"-1","id":367},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"逃避？非也。我既不是年，也不是夕。","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","focus":"-1","id":372},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":374},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#7$1","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"好好好，那我且问你。","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你觊觎这天地，又可知这偌大天地间，到底有什么？","id":377},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#7$1","focus":"-1","id":378},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":380},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":381},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你可知蒙垄的新茶，该是在三月采，还是四月采？","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你可知大漠长夜苦寒时，常唱什么歌，常饮什么酒？","id":383},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你又可知......","id":384},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"-1","id":385},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"......","id":386},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","id":387},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"你对这天地，一无所知。","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"当然，你即是我......","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"枉我们自诩活了这千百年，却依然有太多不知不闻的事，不解不晓的情。","id":390},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":391},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":392},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#9$1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"也曾像山脚酒馆里的那个石匠，连做梦也有忧戚，或者如我那妹妹一样，连梦都不敢做了。","id":395},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"也曾像器伥和墨魉，觉得受限于自己，又受限于天地，总不自由。","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我们这些活了千百年的造物，傲视几十年寿命的芸芸众生，笑他们活得愚昧。归根结底，还是我们更蠢一些。","id":397},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#9$1","focus":"-1","id":398},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"......","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"从南而北，再到这蜀道山巅，于我而言，只不过是一场酣梦。","id":401},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"其实，从太古以来，经过的时间，行过的地方，千年万年，无非是更大的一场梦。","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"这一场大梦做罢，我终于知我是谁——","id":403},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":404},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“岁相”","text":"（无言的轰鸣）","id":406},{"type":"character","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","id":407},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"罢了，说了你也不懂。","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"既不懂，还不走？","id":409},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"既是我的梦，怎么解由我，醉也由我，醒也由我。","id":410},{"type":"Dialog","id":411},{"type":"playSound","key":"$tactfulboost","volume":"0.7","id":412},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g08_pavilion","screenadapt":"coverall","id":414},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":417},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"我既醒来，你又焉在？","id":418},{"type":"dialog","id":419},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":420},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"Character","id":422},{"type":"Image","image":"25_i05","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":423},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":424},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":425},{"type":"Text","text":"醒来。","id":426},{"type":"Text","text":"酒也空了。","id":427},{"type":"Text","text":"好一场梦啊。","id":428},{"type":"Text","text":"我看见了什么？","id":429},{"type":"Text","text":"落日烧透半天的云，三山十八峰，漫漫蜀道，触手即是烟霞。这景色，不曾入画，也不曾入诗。","id":430},{"type":"Text","text":"我看见了什么？","id":431},{"type":"Text","text":"流觞诗会，瓷杯停在了一人又一人面前。漠上长亭，孤烟里，千百人击鼓远征。","id":432},{"type":"Text","text":"既见纵情逍遥的我，也见求全求解、不求甚解的我。梦只是梦，我之为我，都快意。","id":433},{"type":"Text","text":"明明是在这攥江峰顶，无名空地，却仿佛看见了整个大炎。不，是整个太古以来，纵横四方，都如风掠过身侧。","id":434},{"type":"Text","text":"见山却问石，临渊而忘水，原是如此。此地不如就叫“忘水坪”吧。","id":435},{"type":"Text","text":"......","id":436},{"type":"Text","text":"仿佛......还看见了年和夕。呵，既然梦中未见，想必梦外，很快也将再见的。","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"令","text":"呼......日尽水长去......雪落月空留。","id":438},{"type":"dialog","id":439},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":440},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":441},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":442},{"type":"Character","id":443},{"type":"Image","id":444}],"characters":["酒馆伙计","石匠","令","墨魉","器伥","器伥&墨魉","？？？","“岁相”"]}